00:00:06.471 --> 00:00:08.231
Welcome to todays episode

00:00:08.231 --> 00:00:09.900
today I will prepare dopiaza

00:00:11.831 --> 00:00:13.191
for all of my viewers

00:00:13.191 --> 00:00:14.175
the ingredients are as follows

00:00:22.198 --> 00:00:22.838
beef 2 lbs

00:00:22.838 --> 00:00:23.606
onions 1 chopped

00:00:27.260 --> 00:00:27.760
2 whole 

00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:34.060
you can chose between beef or lamb

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:36.080
its completely up to you

00:00:41.886 --> 00:00:42.766
fried onions

00:00:42.966 --> 00:00:46.726
pre fried onions can be bought at your local supermarket

00:00:48.060 --> 00:00:49.580
salt as per your taste.

00:00:54.380 --> 00:00:56.300
I will also prepare the naan.

00:00:57.300 --> 00:00:58.660
Salt yeast and flour.

00:01:10.535 --> 00:01:11.975
I will make the dough.

00:01:18.980 --> 00:01:20.180
Now add the yeast.

00:01:21.440 --> 00:01:22.000
the salt

00:01:25.147 --> 00:01:25.867
1 teaspoon

00:01:30.582 --> 00:01:31.302
some water

00:01:43.372 --> 00:01:45.212
and now slowly add the flour

00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:55.080
slowly add water

00:01:57.195 --> 00:01:58.875
to make the perfect dough

00:02:00.160 --> 00:02:02.080
now the dough is almost ready

00:02:03.626 --> 00:02:04.986
let it rest for 1 hour

00:02:06.881 --> 00:02:08.081
also cover the top

00:02:09.880 --> 00:02:12.600
now we are gonna prepare the beef or soup.

00:02:12.953 --> 00:02:14.473
in the pressure cooker

00:02:14.992 --> 00:02:16.592
heat up your cooking oil

00:02:21.616 --> 00:02:22.816
Now add the onions

00:02:29.100 --> 00:02:31.100
Let the onions to brown up a bit

00:02:42.140 --> 00:02:42.940
keep mixing

00:02:54.900 --> 00:02:55.700
add peprika

00:02:56.048 --> 00:02:57.248
do not add too much

00:02:58.550 --> 00:02:59.910
1 teaspoon is enough

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:01.440
and keep mixing it

00:03:04.546 --> 00:03:05.986
add the garlic powder

00:03:10.420 --> 00:03:11.860
salt as per your taste

00:03:20.706 --> 00:03:21.506
fried onion

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:27.840
and now add the beef

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:30.380
and give it generous amount of stirring

00:03:39.100 --> 00:03:40.620
and add room temp water

00:03:40.620 --> 00:03:41.240
so it cooks evenly

00:03:55.840 --> 00:03:56.720
close the lid

00:03:56.745 --> 00:03:58.825
and pressure cook it for 15 mins

00:04:02.800 --> 00:04:05.120
and now I will prepare the half peas

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:08.520
in a pot add the half peas followed by water

00:04:11.700 --> 00:04:12.200
boiled

00:04:15.901 --> 00:04:16.781
close the lid

00:04:21.060 --> 00:04:25.540
make slices of onions for the mixture that we will be using later on.

00:04:33.944 --> 00:04:35.704
Add onion slices in a bowl.

00:04:41.349 --> 00:04:42.709
Add drips of vinegar

00:04:45.880 --> 00:04:50.920
since vinegar is too stron. I always mix some of boiled room temp water to it.

00:04:53.536 --> 00:04:54.656
this is optional

00:05:05.660 --> 00:05:06.540
beef is ready

00:05:11.100 --> 00:05:17.260
half peas are almost ready. Add a spoon full of the beef soup sauce to the pot for some flavour.

00:05:31.988 --> 00:05:33.668
the dough is almost ready

00:05:45.380 --> 00:05:47.940
it will take 2 mins on each side to cook.

00:05:55.012 --> 00:06:30.000
Serve it however you wish. But this way  is our Traditional Way.

00:06:35.413 --> 00:06:37.173
Very popular Afghan Dish.

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:39.200
You gotta try it.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:44.720
Sweet viewers this was my recipe for the Dopiaza. 

00:06:44.720 --> 00:06:45.480
I hope you all love it and enjoyed this episode. Khuda hafiz.

